headline.main: UN Says 66,000 Displaced in 5 Months of North Syria Fighting
headline.print_headline: UN Says 66,000 Displaced in 5 Months of North Syria Fighting

lead_paragraph: Malaysia said Sunday that its expulsion of North Korea's ambassador was intended to warn Pyongyang that it cannot manipulate the investigation into the killing of the North Korean leader's half brother.
